{"tid":1817281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢2日係台灣總統大選嘅關鍵 我求下你哋幫幫手","createTime":"2020-01-09T03:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T15:06:17.000Z","uid":109780,"like":61,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"4601021293e5f2039f5841d949630c35c701d263","tid":1817281,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nQOcHKZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnQOcHKZ.jpg&h=58696dbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PEY8f4Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPEY8f4Z.jpg&h=8aae9dde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地知唔知台灣大選對勇武手足有幾重要?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eKhpzS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eKhpzS</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>冇錯，台灣大選對手足非常重要！！！<br />\n唔單止係手足，對台灣嘅國際地位亦都好重要！<br />\n台灣有個節目叫關鍵時刻，講咗今次選舉美國好重視<br />\n呢次選舉，唔係藍綠對決咁簡單，係專制獨裁同民主自由之爭<br />\n而蔡英文要嬴的話，</strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">年輕人投票率好重要</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>參考返2018年高雄市長選舉，韓國瑜 vs 民進黨侯選人既比例係<br />\n53.87 vs 44.80</strong> <br />\n<strong>韓國瑜同蔡英文係好大機會55波</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>我哋有3樣野可以做：<br />\n1. 在港手足：用一切方法呼籲台灣人為民主自由投票，(唔好直接講蔡英文/民進黨)<br />\n包括以下途徑：台灣所有Youtuber Channel，Facebook Page，台灣所有IG女神、男神嘅IG Page，所有台灣直播主嘅Channel，包括Twitch等，遊戲內嘅交談平台e.g. 世界頻道/大聲公等<br />\n所有關於蔡英文嘅Youtube片請Like，而韓國瑜嘅請Dislike加Report<br />\n如果手足有打開機，又有入台灣人嘅group，求下你地唔要面咁向佢地宣傳<br />\nDiscord, Line, Skype等等<br />\nSend Message比台灣年輕嘅Youtuber、出名嘅人，叫佢地投票前一日呼籲台灣年輕人出去投票</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 在台手足：學上面2張圖嘅手足咁，去多台灣年輕人嘅地方拉票<br />\n各大夜市等等<br />\n去所有蔡英文嘅競選活動、造勢大會</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 提防三毛分化，包括話蔡英文唔幫手足，由得台灣人揀韓國瑜去死等等嘅消極／分化言論</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>＊一定要叫佢哋珍惜自己嘅一票，以香港與台灣作比較突顯一國兩制之弊，以美國川普嬴大選(台灣叫法)、英國脫歐時年輕人唔投票為鑑，一定要去投票</strong><br />\n<br />\n無論係香港人定台灣人，都一定要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">團結</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港台同行 守護民主 捍衛自由 保衛台灣</span></div>"},{"pid":"7c538b7a01b5a21740219b0a0169ea8e609f7a02","tid":1817281,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:12:16.000Z","msg":"宣傳同拉票啊，小英、民進黨一票不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4323f1f7212a76a2ebd5e215fecb9d06c97778","tid":1817281,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:14:31.000Z","msg":"宣傳同拉票啊，小英、民進黨一票不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6b936285e71558359c3e83da647433088a5c37","tid":1817281,"uid":158404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:14:47.000Z","msg":"開咗兩個post,都無人注意呢個戰場<br />\n幫你推"},{"pid":"16bc117bfd5eb5a25e8fd65dd1e960555f5550fe","tid":1817281,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:19:22.000Z","msg":"宣傳同拉票啊，小英、民進黨一票不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496909702d3bbc3e85f7abc549a4158d304c27ed","tid":1817281,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:24:46.000Z","msg":"宣傳同拉票啊，小英、民進黨一票不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293db920f58ae2521541cf35985204e6784122ee","tid":1817281,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c6b936285e71558359c3e83da647433088a5c37","tid":1817281,"uid":158404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:14:47.000Z","msg":"開咗兩個post,都無人注意呢個戰場<br />\n幫你推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:25:22.000Z","msg":"我打機識好多台灣人，所以好著緊，多謝幫推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a632b95a158faa0603d92ec0aa058ce2c1e404","tid":1817281,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:27:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dfce69e43d